\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes - we used to all sit together and amuse our own selves. 'Course there wasn'
t so much going in as what there is now - and 'course we weren't allowed out in the streets or .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What would you do in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was - by the time we got home from school and - and sometimes we'd take some sums home to do and - we done th
ose and had our tea - in the winter we used to go to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 
Many people divide society into different social classes or groups. In that time, before 1918, did you think of some people belonging to one and some to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Er - I couldn't say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 For instance, would you feel that your schoolteacher was in a different sort of group from your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I suppose they would be really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What about the doctor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well we very often had the doctor in for my father. And for us children as
 well If we were poorly my mother always - get the doctor - and that's one thing she did do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Would you feel that the doctor was in a different social position from your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh yes - I think so. It'd had - they'd have had more - training and 
that, wouldn't they - and more - more - they'd have been better educated than what we were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 
Which group would you say that you belonged to yourself? Would you describe your family as a - what sort of social class would you say your family was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 A very poor class - for one thing - but respectable.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Working class would you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes - respectable working class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 For instance, the doctor and the teacher - what sort of group would you think of that as? Would y
ou be able to give it a name or - how much were you conscious of it when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What - of the doctor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you think of them as being in a different social ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well - he did have a - different station of life to what we were, I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What sort of station of life would you call them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well he'd had more education, wouldn't they, than what we did - better education
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Would you call them upper class or middle class or what do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 They'd be the upper - middle - upper - upper class I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differently from another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No - we always had to treat people the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Were you ever told to curtsy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 We didn't curtsy but we were always told to Sir or Madam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 So you were taught to show respect in some way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Who would that be to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well, the doctor or - or the ladies where we went to work, like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Do you remember anyone showing respect to your parents in these ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No I don't .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 In the district where you lived, who was considered to be the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well - I couldn't say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 In your road - was there anybody more important than you or ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No. I don't think so - no. They were all working class people - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And all much the same - did you feel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What about shopkeepers - who did they associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 You didn't know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What about the clergy - or teachers? Did you know any of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 
Well I know the teachers at school - and Lewis Edwin - they used to have a - er people used to have a shop at the corner of Aden Place there - memorial place now - memorial stones. I think they were some relation to her. She was one of our te
achers at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And you don't know who she was friendly with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 She married a Mr Jenkins. When she got married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And who would he be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 I don't know - I didn't know him at all, really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you know any farmers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you know any employers?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Only what I worked for myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What sort of people would you say went to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Would they be all mixed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I suppose they would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What working class and ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 The doctor and the teacher - would they all go to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 I suppose they would - I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What about the chapel - would that be different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well - chapel people - the Reverend Cowl - I don't know whether you knew him - at Austin Road - he was th
e Clergyman at - er - Congregation Church. And the Colebrook}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2062579\charrsid14358847 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 s so they were Congregational - we knew them and - er -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 They were shopkeepers weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes. And Pimm and Boughtons they ..... They were ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 They were shopkeepers too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes - they were Congregational.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 So you can't say really whether it was different from the chapel or the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Where you lived, did you - all the people in the working class have the same standard of living or were there, would you say
, there were different groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I suppose there were some different groups - they perhaps - earned a little bit more money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 If they had a little bit more money then they would have lived a little differently.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes. Well I suppose they would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Do you think that one group thought itself superior to the rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No - I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you know a family that was different from your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Were some families thought of as rough and others as respectable? I thin
k you said that you felt that your family belonged to a respectable working class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes - but they all seemed to be respectable in Falcon Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 The rough families would live somewhere else would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well they - 
there was some children came to school - they were a bit on the rough, side, you know, 'course I don't know what their parents were like. But I don't think any children that went to school when we went to school - were allowed to go eat and do the things 
that the children of today do. They were all made to go in at a certain time and - don't remember any children - allowed to run the streets like they run the streets now.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Do you remember a distinction such as being rough and respectable between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Would they treat people differently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Think they'd treat them all the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 All the same - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was it possible at that time to move from one group to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 You can't remember anyone who did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Do you remember anyone being described or you describing them yourself, as a real gentleman or a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 If you had, what sort of a person would you think that would be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well, I think the more educated people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And how would they show that they were a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well you can always sort of tell can't you - that's how I think myself. If they're - more sort of educated than what you are yourself.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 In what sort of way can you tell? Is it the way they speak or the way they behave or ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I suppose the way they speak and the way they behave.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Do you think then of say, a real lady, having good manners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well they should have if they - been well educated and - more educated than what the - poorer class are.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Do you remember seeing a policeman around where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh yes - there was very often about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What did you feel - think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I didn't take much notice.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 When you were naughty did your mother ever say call a policeman'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How do you think he treated the people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I didn't have much to with 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was your home rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you see anything of your landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well, it changed hands so much - they - yes - they used to call for the rent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 But different people called did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Different people called - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Do you remember what you felt about it when they called for the rent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I didn't used to think anything - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 You just accepted it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 I accepted that they called - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Do you remember feeling that your parents had to struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 When you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes they did - very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And you realised that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did it - what did you think of it? As a child. Did it worry you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well, it did when I was getting older - I left school and I understood things more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What difference did it make to the family when your father was ill or out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 
He was - he was never out of work - it was only 'cos he was out of work when he was ill. But he was never out of work - not - er - because he was out of a job no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And that was fairly often you said when he had asthma and bronchitis?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you ever get help from the Guardians or the Parish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Or any charity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Were you given lessons by one of your parents or anyone else before you went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 About five years old, I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 When you first started - can you remember what time in the morning you went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 We had to get there at nine o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And if you came back to lunch, what time would you come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 We'd come out at twelve.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And then would you go back to afternoon school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And what time would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 About half past one. Come out about four to half past.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What kind of school was it that you went to - was that Holy Trinity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No - it was the - er - the South - what they call the Southill - at the top of the - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 It was then called Southill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes. It was only a small school and Southill was built as colours came down to Sandfield.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was it a board school or a church school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Board school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Were there boys and girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 The boys were on one side of the road and the girls on the other - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 So your school was a girls school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How did you get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 We used to have to walk when we were at Southill and of course we weren't very far away from Southill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How long would that take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh about - about - I should think about twenty minutes to half an hour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And who went with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh we always - all went together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No grown up with you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well - my sister was older than what we were you see and .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 So she looked after you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 But your mother didn't go with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No she didn't go with us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Where did you have your mid-day meal then - did you have it mainly at school or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No we used to - in the summer - all the summer we went home. But in the winter if it was very bad we used to take sandwiches.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And you could stay at school and eat them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What did you think of school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh I - I used to like school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How did you feel about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well some were very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did the teachers emphasise certain things as important in life? Such as manners.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No I don't think so but ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Tidiness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well it - oh yes they used to - er - teach us to be very tidy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And ways of speaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 If you did something the teachers disapproved of, what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well - we used to stay in and write lines.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How did they punish the children? Would it always be this sort of punishment or were there sometimes something else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well if you were very bad I think you were caned.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And that was the girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 The girls as well as the boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 The boys were the same were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 But not very }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2062579\charrsid14358847 often}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
