\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 You feel you taught yourself as much as they taught you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 I ta
ught me - yes - at school - we - we didn't learn much at school in regards to service I don't think. In fact there was more people - children leaving school and going into service then than what there is now. There's not that things now - what they call s
ervants years ago - but I don't regret having to go to service myself, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 While you were at school did you have a part time job or any means of earning a little regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Can you remember your first full time job? After you left school. That would be in service.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 
Well not - I can't remember the first living in job - but I remember, I think, the first one - when I left school I went to a place just for - eight months - and - er - the lady only wanted me for those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What would you do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 
I used to do housework. And then I left there and I went to - was nanny to a little girl. And I used to go from eight o'clock to six in the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How did you get the job, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 I think somebody recommended me - but I couldn't tell you who.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Not through your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 You had to look after this little girl and do the housework. Do you remember what hours you worked?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 From - er - eight o'clock in the morning to six at night. I used to have to wait to put her to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you work on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you have a half day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Er - sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Do you remember what you were paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Five shillings when I first started there. Five shillings per ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Per week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you feel that that was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I - I - I suppose I did because they weren't paying the wage then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Do you think it was about the same as other girls'.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 About the same - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 I give it to my mother, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 All of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Do you know what she used it for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Housekeeping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How did you get on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 She did buy my clothes, you see, I didn't buy my own clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh she bought your clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And put it into housekeeping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes, well she didn't have much to put in the housekeeping after she bought my clothes, did she? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2062579\charrsid14358847 She had }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 to keep me respectable for going in ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you have special clothes to wear for your work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No. Used to have to wear aprons you see, had to wear ....
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And she had to buy those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How did you get on with the people you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And how did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well she was very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How did you feel about her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well, I was very fond of her and the girl - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How did you like the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 I didn't have to do much work - I looked after the litt
le girl, you see, then she had another baby while I was there and I used to have to take them both out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Do you remember how you felt about the work? Were you pleased to have that job? Did you like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes, I did, yes. 'Cos I was very fond of children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did the job alter your attitude to school in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What did you do after you finished the eight months in that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 The first one - that was the eight months - then I went to the little girl - I done the whole day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh that was the next one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes. I went for the whole day. I was there about three years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And you were still living at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes - daily - yes. Then I think I took a all day job - living in job then. I can't think exactly where that was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Were there any other servants there apart from yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No - only myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Where did you sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Upstairs in a bedroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Would it be up in an attic?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No - oh no, in a bedroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 You'd have a bedroom to yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And where did you eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 In the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was there anywhere that you could sit when you were not working.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No only in the kitchen.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did the mistress supervise all the housework personally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Or did she leave you to .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh no - she used to let me to get on with it - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you feel at ease with members of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How did the members of the family address each other and you? What would they call you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh they used to call me by my Christian name.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What would you call them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Just Madam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you feel that any of them was interested in you as a person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well - some was and some just interested in you doing your work I think. In those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Do you remember that particular one when you were living in the first one what your employer was like - was she interested in you at all?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh I think she was interested in me, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did your mistress give any moral guidance to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Were you allowed at any time to do just what you liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well in the evenings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 They were your own were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes. After dinner at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 When could you go out of the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 One evening a week. And every other Sunday. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did your employer mind what you did when you went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh no. I used to go home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you have to be back at a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes. Ten o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Can you remember if you felt home-sick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Were you lonely?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh at times. But I usually got over - when I want to live in - I used to get - got in with some very nice people. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 You mean your employer - the family was nice?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was there anything you particularly liked or disliked about that job, the first one when you were living in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 
No. I can't remember which - hardly - which one I went - not to live in first. 'Cos I had a few jobs because I wasn't very strong. And I used to have to go home with treatment for }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2062579\charrsid14358847 anaemia}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847  very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And did you have to have a rest from work then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 I had to have a rest from work, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How did the housework go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh I didn't mind housework at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was the washing sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Er - in one place it - it was not - only just the sheets - I had to do all the other with a dolly tub.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was that only in one of your jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 That's one of my jobs - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Who made or mended the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh I think they used to do that themselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Who did the cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 I did the cooking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Who was responsible for repairs and improvements to a house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I suppose their own selves, really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 This first job that you had when you were living in, can you remember whether you helped with the children there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I ca
n only remember which was in my first job - that's to live in. Only I had one - er - job where I was a nurse to a - another little boy - but I was only there five months because - er - they came home from India. They lived with her - her people while they
 were in England.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And that was a temporary job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 
That was a temporary job. And - er we went up to Scotland in the - they was home you see from India - and I took this little boy over and lived with her people while we were in - in Guildford. Then 
we went up to - er - Scotland - and the gentleman's people went up there - and took their maids. So we went up with them you see. When I came back I was so ill I had to go home again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you have to work very hard?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No I 
didn't - I only had - only had the baby to look after. But we went right up Caithness and Wick and that was too cold for me, you see. So I came - we came back in the beginning of October and - er - we arrived in Guildford on the Monday night and on the Th
u
rsday I had to go home. So I didn't go back to them - they went back to India - you see - before I was well enough to go back. But the lady did ask for the - when I first went with her - if - er - I would like to go to India with them, but I'd have to sta
y for four years. My mother didn't want me to go. Course I shouldn't have gone because you see I was ill.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Can you tell me about one of your jobs where you were living in, can you remember a particular one that you could talk to me about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well th
e last job that I ever had and that was - I went there in 1935 - later - and - er - I lived in - I was with the lady five years - and she had a little baby boy - 'cos I done cooking and housework and everything there - and she had a little baby boy - 1940
 - and that was him their now - in the photo - and I looked after him 'til he went to a boarding school. But I had to do housework cooking and everything then 'cos during the war you couldn't get no maids.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Can I ask you a little bit about that? What about your duties - that was to run the house and to look after the little boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And you were living in so what off time did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well - I sometimes used to have a afternoon and evening a week. And 'course the lady used to look after the baby.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 When you went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 
Yes - I used to have to do things before I went out. Before we - before - that wasn't in Guildford. They lived in Turney Green - that's where I met the lady - then we went to Millford - that's the time I left Guilf
ord a bit. We went to Millford and then they - they left there and they went down to Brighton during the war - and er - 'course that when the baby was small - and 'course we only lived in a flat then at Brighton - that was during the war - then he bought 
a house at - er - Clayton - and I lived there with them. Then moved around a bit then, you see, with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What about the child, did he spend much time with his parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Not very much. I had him more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was there a regular time when he'd see them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well the gentleman was in the Navy, you see - the baby was born and he was - I think he was abroad when the baby was born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Would the baby be with his mother at certain times of the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well - she'd have him sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 But you would have him most of the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 But I would have him most of the time. Sometimes she'd, you know, she'd come out and say she'd bath him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 But did you ordinarily bath him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And dress him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Every night - yes. Bath him every night - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What about playing games with him and taking him out? -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh I used to take him out every afternoon - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And what about the shopping?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well - we used to - er - get .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Arrange that between you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Arrange that bet
ween us, you see, I used to take him sometimes shopping with me, when we lived at Clayton - the other side of Brighton - we used to - er - I used to walk to Hassocks with him and in the afternoon do the shopping. And 'course before I left you see he was -
 he could walk and run about and ..... And then he went to a boarding school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was there a nursery in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 When the little boy saw his mother, would he go down to the sitting room or would he stay in the nursery or ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh no - he'd go down in the sitting room with her - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Would the mother be working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did the little boy have any tasks to carry out regularly to help in the house as he got bigger?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What time did he go to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I use
d to start running - when he was home - I - when he was little - I used to start running his bath about half past five - quarter to six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And did you always put him to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And what age would he be when he put himself to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well he didn't put himself to bed - while I had him - I used to - he went to the boarding school before he was eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did the little boy share the bedroom or the bed with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No. No he had a nursery all - on his own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And did you have a room to yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And then the parents would have another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And what room would be used for bathing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Beg Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What room would be used for bathing the child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well we had - yes we had two bathrooms in most places.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How often did the little boy have a bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Every evening.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And how often were clean clothes put on him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh - nearly every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And where did the grown ups eat their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 In the dining room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And what about the little boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well he - used to - er - have them in the nursery with me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 With you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Would you have your meals with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes. Sometimes he'd go down - er - when he got older he used to go down into the dining room with his mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was that any special occasion or .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No - very often we used to - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 So you had your meals at the same time as he did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What cooking equipment was there in that house, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 W
ell there was - at a - she had a - she had an electric stove and - er - after that we always had - I always had an electric stove too cook on. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What time did you have breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I used to get Richard up about eight o'clock for his breakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Who would be there at breakfast time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh we just had our breakfast on our own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Just you and the little boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What about his mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well his - his father - 'cos his father was in the Navy - Naval - and his mother - well sometimes I used to take hers up to her bedroom.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you take it up for her or did she ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Cook it herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No, no I'd take it up for her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What would you have for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I - usually I didn't have very 
much 'cos I'm not a big breakfast eater - but I used to give Richard an egg and porridge or a rasher or - when he got old enough to eat it, like.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And what about his mother - would she have the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Sometimes she'd have an egg - sometimes she just had toast and marmalade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you have anything different on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No - just the same, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And what would you have for lunch - would you have a main meal in the middle of the day for the child or would you have it in the evening?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Main meal for us all in the middle of the day - and I'd cook at night for the lady again - and when he was home ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 You'd cook the meal in the middle of the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What sort of a meal would it be in the evening? What would you cook for her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well something light if she was on her own but - er - if the gentleman was home well perhaps they'd have a few - full course dinner.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Then you'd have two main meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Were any of the following made in the house - bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 
No. Well we - we did make some jam one year and that's before the baby was born - and we had a cook for a little while - and I done the house - parlour work when ..... and this cook made some jam. But they weren't very big jam eaters at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What about bottled fruit and vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 They always had their own vegetables. 'Cos they had - she had a good gardener.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was it ever bottled -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 The baby had a bottle - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No - the vegetables - were they ever bottled?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh no - they weren't bottled - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Or the fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What about pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No they didn't make any pickles.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Any wine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Or beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Herbal remedies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was there any fruit grown as well as the vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh yes - we had plenty of fruit - apples and pears.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you have to buy anything as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No, not usually.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Any tinned or dried vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No - we didn't have a lot of that sort of stuff.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And they had somebody to look after the garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was any livestock kept for the family - like hens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well we would only have - er - if - believe it or believe it not we was getting quite a little farm yard over there - yes. She - 
she got two pigs, and a cow and - er - she had two horses - she used to go hunting - they had money - and - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Any hens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh yes. Plenty of chicken we had - our own eggs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Goats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No, no goats. Had all our own eggs when we were at Millford - that was the only place where we had it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Who looked after all these animals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well we had a groom gardner you see - he used to look after ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And he did it all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How many times a week was meat eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Ooh I think every day - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was any tinned meat used?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did the children or the little boy and you and the parents have the same food or was it different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No we had the same food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 I think you said that you often had your meal with him in the nursery when he was small.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Then went down to the dining room when he was bigger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 With his mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was the little boy allowed to talk at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No - er - really he was very good. I must say I
 - not say - 'cos I looked after him but he was - he was very good. And I didn't have no - all the time he was teething or - I never - I never had a bad night with him - 'cos I used to have to get up if he was, but - and he slept in his own nursery.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And as he got older and learnt to talk - could he talk to you at meals - was he allowed to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well he - he didn't - worry you - he was such a - er - slow eater and he couldn't talk or anything 'cos he was too busy with his meal.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Could he choose what he wanted to eat from what was cooked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh no he had to eat .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Had to have a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What was said if something was left uneaten on the plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well he didn't usually leave anything, 'cos if we were in the din
ing room with his mother, his mother would make him eat it - which I think sometimes - with a child like that - they don't - can't always expect them to eat it - everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Would you be a little more lenient than his mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I suppose I was really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 If there was something on the table out of reach, like the salt, could he ask someone to pass it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 He would ask.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Could he ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well he - I don't think he ever wanted it - he was a small eater and - when he was little.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was he taught to hold his knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And sit in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Could toys or books be brought to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 When could they leave the table - when could he leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well he had to wait 'til we'd finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Until everybody had finished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
