\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No I think she still give it to the child fi
rst 'cos he was a - well we didn't very often have it with them - if - if they did I used to have mine after on my own - if the gentleman were home.
