\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 So he knew that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
