hat - er - college and that - and he went through to be a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1343443\charrsid14358847 veterinary}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847  surgeon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
