\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Or behaving politely?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 All this sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you teach the child what you thought was important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
