Yes I can - when he was - although it was their fault really, her sister and - and she took him for a - a - into a swim, you know, into a paddling pool - and of course it was their fault really - he was only t
iny - they put him on the steps - they'd had him in the pool - they put him on the steps and he slipped in. 'Course she thought it was his fault and - 'course it was not really because they shouldn't have put him on the wet slip - steps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Could you tel
l me a little bit about the house that you worked in in Sydney Road - I think you said that your employer there was a Mrs Hayes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And were you the only servant there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes - that's - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And where did you sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh I had a nice little bedroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was it right up in the attic?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No, no, just an ordinary bedroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And where did you eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 'Course I had to eat in the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 In the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was there anywhere you could sit when you were not working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No - only the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did your mistress supervise all the housework personally or did she leave it to you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh - yes - she left it to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 She left it to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you feel at ease with her and members of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes I was very - in fact I was very fond of the daughter - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 You got on well with the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh yes I got on very well with the family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How did you and the members of the family address each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I - er - she didn't expect me to call her Madam - I used to call her Mrs Hayes and him - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And what did they call you - by your Christian name?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 My Christian name.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you feel that any of them was interested in you as a person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I think she did 'cos - er - I was with her quite a long time - three years or over. Over three years - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And this was before 1917 when you were ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did your mistress give any moral guidance to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Were you allowed to do just what you liked at any time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well, you know - it was the same as anyone would be in service - just have my half days and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And what about the evening when you finished work. Could you do what you liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh yes - but not go out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 But not go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 When could you go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Just the - er - my Thursday afternoons - my Sundays and er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you have every Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No - every other Sunday - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was that half a day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Half a day. And sometimes Saturday - used to go out - and the shops used to be open then. And I - she'd send me down shopping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 For yourself or for her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No - for her.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Could you do shopping for yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did your mistress mind what you did when you went out on your half day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 That was left entirely to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes. I always went home to my parents.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 You went home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How did the housework go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well sometimes very hard 'cos I wasn't very strong.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 You found it quite hard did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes. At times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was the washing sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No - I had to do that at home. Except the sheets - they went - but - took them to the laundry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 But you did the rest of the family's washing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes - and my own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Who made or mended the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well they used to do - the needlework - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Who did the cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 I did the cooking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Who was responsible for repairs and improvements to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well, didn't have much improvements to the house not while I was there - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you ever feel homesick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No - 'cos I was in Guildford and I saw my parents - often - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Were you lonely?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No - 'cos we - er - Miss Hayes used to very often come down and have a chat to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 This was one of the daughters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes. The daughter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 How old would she be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 She was fourteen when I first went there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 A schoolgirl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Uh - huh
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was there anything you particularly liked or disliked about the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Did you have any responsibility for the young people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Can you tell me where the family ate their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 In the dining room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And I presume that the young people and the parents ate their meals all together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Were there any exceptions to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What cooking equipment was there in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 I think it was a kitchener.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Was it? Coal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes - it was - er - it was underground.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And you had to cook with a coal range?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 When was breakfast eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 In the dining room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 What sort of time would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Well I used to get them - about half past eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 And what members of the family would be present at breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 The gentleman and the daughter and son - lady usually had hers up in the bedroom 'cos she wasn't very strong.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 So it would just be the father and the two young people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079523 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 When did the mother have her breakfast then - at the same time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8878128 RN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1523697\charrsid14358847 At the same time.
